        <p><span facs="#zone_40239e6e-c398-11e8-b47d-f40f243b5e05">23</span><span facs="#zone_4023a054-c398-11e8-8204-f40f243b5e05">父と母送る極二つ</span><span facs="#zone_4023a164-c398-11e8-abd6-f40f243b5e05">けふ踊る絵日記軍露の英霊と死秘めた軍國の妻</span><span facs="#zone_4023a254-c398-11e8-a5d8-f40f243b5e05">親の模型せめて遺骨にお供へ</span><span facs="#zone_4023a350-c398-11e8-bbc5-f40f243b5e05">谷風玉川奨端町二の五四一に</span><span facs="#zone_4023a428-c398-11e8-bd10-f40f243b5e05">「</span><span facs="#zone_4023a4fa-c398-11e8-93c5-f40f243b5e05">藤一は母なき家庭</span><span facs="#zone_4023a5da-c398-11e8-b1eb-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_4023a6ac-c398-11e8-86f0-f40f243b5e05">しかも二つの松</span><span facs="#zone_4023a786-c398-11e8-86e5-f40f243b5e05">を一と時にでくる軍國の兄妹と</span><span facs="#zone_4023a858-c398-11e8-b4a9-f40f243b5e05">田要とながらの門標を掲げ</span><span facs="#zone_4023a928-c398-11e8-a943-f40f243b5e05">なった</span><span facs="#zone_4023a9fa-c398-11e8-b243-f40f243b5e05">!</span><span facs="#zone_4023aacc-c398-11e8-a2d1-f40f243b5e05">た家に踊る</span><span facs="#zone_4023ab9e-c398-11e8-bc9a-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_4023ac70-c398-11e8-8c73-f40f243b5e05">そして</span><span facs="#zone_4023ad50-c398-11e8-aa9c-f40f243b5e05">等を迎えるその前夜</span><span facs="#zone_4023ae22-c398-11e8-b60c-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_4023aef4-c398-11e8-8de1-f40f243b5e05">梅雨上り</span><span facs="#zone_4023afcc-c398-11e8-bfeb-f40f243b5e05">事暴記念日の来る七月七</span><span facs="#zone_4023b09e-c398-11e8-8f12-f40f243b5e05">の奥澤の町に</span><span facs="#zone_4023b170-c398-11e8-ad73-f40f243b5e05">日</span><span facs="#zone_4023b242-c398-11e8-9007-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_4023b314-c398-11e8-aad6-f40f243b5e05">故軍盤の夫人美津</span><span facs="#zone_4023b3e6-c398-11e8-9d60-f40f243b5e05">(</span><span facs="#zone_4023b4c6-c398-11e8-892f-f40f243b5e05">常時州八</span><span facs="#zone_4023b598-c398-11e8-8065-f40f243b5e05">二人の兄妹</span><span facs="#zone_4023b670-c398-11e8-b75c-f40f243b5e05">を訪ねる</span><span facs="#zone_4023b742-c398-11e8-acf5-f40f243b5e05">、